  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Validation experiments were performed across five flow-speed operating points; results are reported inline. Note: generation activity provenance is recorded for selected validation results only — general experimental campaigns are referenced narratively for the remaining results.",
