      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence criteria and floating-point round-off effects must be assessed and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence to 1e-5 is reported but no formal assessment of iterative error magnitude relative to discretization error was performed. Factor flagged as not-assessed at MRL 5; achieved level 1."
    },
    {
