      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented review of analyst setup decisions (boundary condition selection, turbulence model choice, UDF parameterisation) by an independent reviewer.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup was conducted. The hemolysis power-law coefficients were selected by the primary analyst without documented justification of the specific values used. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
