      "acceptanceCriteria": "The turbulence model and hemolysis damage model must be justified for the flow regime present in the pump, with sensitivity to model-form choices quantified.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model is used; selection is justified by prior literature for rotating machinery. The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen coefficients) is applied without sensitivity analysis to alternative coefficient sets or model forms. Achieved level 2."
    },
