      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition inputs must have documented sources with uncertainty ranges; Monte Carlo sampling must cover the full input uncertainty space.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on inlet flow rate and rotational speed. Blood viscosity and density were treated as fixed nominal values. Hematocrit variability, which affects hemolysis susceptibility, was not included in the UQ sampling. Achieved level 2."
