      "acceptanceCriteria": "A formal equivalency assessment must demonstrate that the validation experiment input parameters (geometry, fluid, operating conditions) are sufficiently representative of the COU inputs to support extrapolation of validation evidence.",
      "rationale": "No equivalency assessment was conducted between the FDA generic pump validation configuration and the proprietary VAD COU configuration. This is the most significant credibility gap identified for COU2 at MRL 5."
